title: Fixed issue: go to Preferences and disable a connector that supports…
message: Fixed issue: go to Preferences and disable a connector that supports bootstrapping (e.g. Comtube), return to main screen, then the progress bar does not stop. This is because WebSMS doesn't know yet that this connector is disabled and sends the RUN_BOOTSTRAP, the connector however is already disabled so it ignores the request and does not reply.

title: Send RUN_UPDATE only to connectors that can process it. Was issue: ConnectorSMS…
